PAD 1.0
=======

1- Prepare and build PAD on Linux
---------------------------------

Download and extract latest apr version in this directory

Update files prepare.sh and CMakeLists.txt with APR directory name.

Type:
# ./prepare
# ./make


2- Prepare and build PAD on Windows
-----------------------------------

Start the Visual Studio command prompt and type the following commands:

> prepare.bat
> cd build
> nmake -f Makefile pad 